transcripts: The versatile Lasko tower fan is ideal for any living room and even dorm room. Standing at 36 inches this tower fan with remote control provides white noise as well as options for quiet circulation. Featuring electronic control operation, a programmable timer, smooth isolation in 3 quiet speeds. This fan is as customizable as it is functional. An easy grip handle and patent fused safety plug allows for easy transport and ensures safety making Lasko tower fan the perfect addition to any living space.
